<div class="container">

  <div class="card card-outline-primary text-center p-4">
      <h3 class="card-title">How to use the Qu4tro API</h3>
      <div class="card-block">
        <div class="card card-outline-info mb-3 text-center">
          
          <h5 class="card-text">/api/quiz/&lt quiz id &gt</h5>
          <div class="card-block">
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>GET route for getting all of the questions for quiz ID passed.  Passing the quiz ID is mandatory.</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center">
          <div class="card-block">
            <h5 class="card-text">/api/quizzes/&lt user ID &gt</h5>
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>GET route for getting all of the quizzes for user ID passed.  Passing the user ID is mandatory.</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card card-outline-primary text-center p-4 my-4">
      <h3 class="card-title">Admin RESTful routes</h3>
      <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
      * This would not show on the public page but only for app administrators. This is shown now for testing and presentation only
      </blockquote>

      <div class="card-block">  <!-- create question -->
        <!-- ______________________________________________________________________ -->
        <div class="card card-outline-info mb-3 text-center"> <!-- create question -->
          <h5 class="card-text">/questionMaker</h5>
          <div class="card-block">
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>CREATE route for creating a new question through your form.  Make sure that a quiz id, question are included in your form</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center"><!-- create answer/update question with answer -->  
          <h5 class="card-text">/answers</h5>
          <div class="card-block">
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>UPDATE route for creating a question through your form.  Make sure to include a question Id and answer in your form</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center"> <!-- update question -->
          <h5 class="card-text">/api/question/&lt question ID &gt</h5>          
          <div class="card-block">
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>PUT route for updating question with question ID passed.  Passing the question ID is mandatory.</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>          
        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center"> <!-- delete question --> 
          <h5 class="card-text">/api/question</h5>
          <div class="card-block">
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>DELETE route for deleting a question through your form.  Make sure to include a question Id in your form</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center"> <!-- create quiz -->
          <div class="card-block">
            <h5 class="card-text">/newQuiz</h5>
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>CREATE route for creating new quiz. Make sure to include user ID and quiz name in your form.</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center"> <!-- delete quiz -->
          <div class="card-block">
            <h5 class="card-text">/api/quiz/&lt quiz ID &gt</h5>
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>DELETE route for deleting quiz with quiz ID passed.  Passing the quiz ID is mandatory.  Make sure to delete all questions linked to this quiz first.</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>  
        <div class="card card-outline-primary mb-3 text-center"> <!-- update quiz -->
          <div class="card-block">
            <h5 class="card-text">/api/quiz/&lt quiz ID &gt</h5>
            <blockquote class="card-blockquote">
              <p>PUT route for updating quiz with quiz ID passed.  Passing the quiz ID is mandatory.  Make sure to include quiz ID and quiz name.</p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>                
      </div>
  </div>

